      </mod></line>
    <line rend="indent1">And sate as thus upon that slope of <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">d</del>
        <add place="intralinear">l</add>
      </mod>awn</line>
    <line>Under the self same bough, &amp; heard as there</line>
    <line rend="indent1">The birds the fountains &amp; the Ocean hold</line>
    <line>Sweet talk in <del rend="strikethrough">the</del> music through the enamoured air.</line>
    <line rend="indent1">And then a Vision on my brain was rolled ..</line>
